  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: e2d12754d13c346428d90eee7fd68121, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Logic_NoteText
  noteTitle: FROZEN HORIZON
  noteContent: 'The water washes nothing away.

    To find what was buried, you
    must seek the window that never opens. Where the sky is woven from oil, and the
    trees stand paralyzed in time.

    Tear away the illusion of the quiet landscape...
    the real rot festers behind the wooden frame.'
